    "In contrast, our approach is able to avoid the yellow cuboids based on the noisy estimated depth.",
    "We do not use MonoNav's 3D reconstruction; trajectories are overlaid solely for visualization and comparison.",
    "2 in (1a) penalizes large control inputs, and the weights w i tune the robot's riskseeking behavior.",
    "Control bounds are enforced through (1b).",
    "We construct a MPC feedback loop by solving (1a)-(1b) in a receding horizon manner from the current state."
